---
title: Miso Baked Aubergine with Pickled Cucumber and Brown Rice
description: We love a good Miso Aubergine with  Rice and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/miso-baked-aubergine-b68e06ce-a40105e1.jpg
